<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Chernobyl_placement.svg" class="image" title="Location of the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Chernobyl_placement.svg/180px-Chernobyl_placement.svg.png" width="180" height="138" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
